summary: A revision of the original New Presets mod with minor or major differences to the humanoid presets of the mod. (Green-Fins and Haile will not be changed.)
descriptionHtml:
Exactly as it says in the brief description.

For a complete list of changes:

Isolde - Softer makeup for ENB's, a more ragged hairstyle and different eyes
Anna- Completely freckled all over her body, more vibrant skin color and hair color, natural makeup (requires Frecklemania1)
Maria- Looks more like a redguard and removed the warpaint
Elise - Different makeup colors, and a different eye color
Drasphore- New name: Xena, and looks a lot more human!
Lillith - Looks a lot more like a human
Lisel- New hairstyle, new makeup
Ula-Ula - Generally a prettier orc with new everything.

To make them look exactly like the screenshots, use:

1.  SG textures
2.  SG eyebrows
3.  SG hairstyles 268 or 350
4.  Frecklemania (not Frecklemania 2)
5. The Eyes of Beauty

Bodyslide Preset I use: Modified Amazon (My own)
